14:                  Property Subject To Section 19(8)   995 0.004767061
15:                     Storage & Warehousing (Closed)   908 0.004350242
16:    Duplex, Non-Strata Side by Side or Front / Back   891 0.004268795
17:                       Store(S) And Living Quarters   859 0.004115483
18:                      Office Building (Primary Use)   629 0.003013549
19:                               Store(S) And Offices   595 0.002850654
